<li id="cite_note-21"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/africa/article4168245.ece" class="external text" title="http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/africa/article4168245.ece" rel="nofollow">We agree that you are black, South African court tells Chinese</a>, The Times</li>
</ol>
